   void Interleaved()

     Make this screen an Interleaved screen (the value TRUE will be used as data for
     the attribute SA_Interleaved).


   void ToFront()

     Bring the screen to front.


   void ToBack()

    Bring the screen to back.


   UWORD Depth()

