     The default parameter for @{I}Width@{UI} is 0.


   void FGPen(LONG pen)

     Foreground pen to use for the current label text (text passed as parameter in
     method @{I}Text@{UI} before this call).

     Default pen value is 1.


   void BGPen(LONG pen);

     Background pen to use for the current label text (text passed as parameter in
     method @{I}Text@{UI} before this call).

     Default pen value is 0.


   void Mode(UBYTE mode)

     Draw mode to use for the current label text (text passed as parameter in
     method @{I}Text@{UI} before this call).

